I hope you like the map!

Some info; The teleport with on top of the white surf box (see screenshot 3) randomly switches between two destinations. I did this to spice up gameplay. 

Uhm, beyond that there isn't much to say about the map really. I hope you find it fun and creative. If I know you on steam and you have a server, let me know if you put it on there? I'd like to play some combat with others. : )
